      <title>布林肯访问黎巴嫩推动中东停火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-22/blinken-in-lebanon-to-push-for-mideast-cease-fire-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯周一启程前往中东，这是他第 11 次访问中东，自一年多前以色列遭受袭击以来，他一直试图促成以色列与伊朗支持的武装分子之间的停火，但未能成功。彭博新闻社的保罗·华莱士与詹妮弗·扎巴萨贾就“中东和非洲视野”进行了讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-22/blinken-in-lebanon-to-push-for-mideast-cease-fire-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 04:35:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>现代印度公司首次公开募股 (IPO) 创下历史新高，有望上市交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-22/hyundai-india-set-to-trade-after-record-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国现代汽车公司的高管出席其印度子公司的上市仪式。现代汽车印度有限公司的股票即将开始交易，该公司进行了 33 亿美元的首次公开募股，这是南亚国家有史以来规模最大的首次公开募股。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-22/hyundai-india-set-to-trade-after-record-ipo</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 04:28:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场对美联储降息存疑，债券市场一片混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-10-22/fed-cuts-helter-skelter-in-bond-markets-as-doubts-harden</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国债收益率回升至 4% 以上。责怪鲍威尔，责怪特朗普，但不要假装选举已经结束。事实并非如此。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-10-22/fed-cuts-helter-skelter-in-bond-markets-as-doubts-harden</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 04:18:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国将继续对俄罗斯液化天然气出口“收紧限制”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/us-will-continue-to-tighten-the-screws-on-russian-lng-exports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务院最高能源官员称，美国将继续“加大对俄罗斯液化天然气出口的限制”，以切断莫斯科用于乌克兰战争的资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/us-will-continue-to-tighten-the-screws-on-russian-lng-exports</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 04:03:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲反复出现的经济噩梦——特朗普的选举胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/a-second-trump-presidency-worries-europe-central-bankers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[各国央行行长们担心，唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫后将引发新一轮贸易战，这将使他们的工作变得更加困难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/a-second-trump-presidency-worries-europe-central-bankers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 04:00:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汽车制造商陷入两年来首次欧洲销售下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/automakers-are-mired-in-first-europe-sales-slump-in-two-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于欧洲经济持续停滞且消费者削减支出，9 月份欧洲汽车销量出现两年多来连续首次月度下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/automakers-are-mired-in-first-europe-sales-slump-in-two-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员重新考虑美联储路径，债券普遍遭遇抛售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/bonds-are-selling-off-everywhere-as-traders-trim-rate-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者担心美国降息步伐放缓，从澳大利亚到日本的债券价格都在下跌，这一趋势有可能颠覆各地的债务状况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/bonds-are-selling-off-everywhere-as-traders-trim-rate-cut-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 02:22:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>现代汽车印度公司首次公开募股 (IPO) 募资 33 亿美元，首日股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/hyundai-motor-india-set-to-debut-after-nation-s-largest-ever-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[现代汽车印度有限公司 (Hyundai Motor India Ltd.) 的股价在孟买首次公开募股 (IPO) 上市初期一度下跌 2.6%，对于今年全球最活跃的首次公开募股 (IPO) 场所之一来说，这是一个低迷的开局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/hyundai-motor-india-set-to-debut-after-nation-s-largest-ever-ipo</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 01:15:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>东京地铁上市将测试日本股票市场兴趣</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/tokyo-metro-s-listing-to-test-appetite-for-japanese-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[东京地铁公司运营着全球最大的地铁系统之一，其首次公开募股将测试日本股市的牛市前景，因为该公司的公开募股获得了超额认购。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/tokyo-metro-s-listing-to-test-appetite-for-japanese-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 00:35:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券市场延续抛售势头，亚洲股市下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员认为美联储在今年剩余时间内降息的预期正在降温，亚洲股市和债券市场连续第二天下跌。]]></description>
